### How to Ask Good Questions

Include:
- Which exercise/project you're working on
- What you expected to happen
- What actually happens
- What you've already tried
- Clear photos of your circuit (top view, good lighting)
- Schematic if you have one

Good example:
```
Module 1, Exercise 2
Problem: My CD4026 isn't counting. Display stays at 0.
What I tried: 
- Verified 5V on pin 16, GND on pin 8
- Checked clock signal with LED - it's blinking
- Reset pin (15) is connected to GND
Photo: [attached breadboard image]
```

Bad example:
```
"It doesn't work help"
```
